{"tid":136946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶1個睡袋兩份瞓 年輕露宿者倍增","createTime":"2017-02-27T12:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T08:30:21.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd81290ca7f914b9ccecbfe2742a716a5ef7dc70","tid":136946,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】無綫真人騷《有樓萬事足》引起全城熱話，拜金港女的金句是「有樓才有真愛」，但現實生活中，有無殼青年要淪落露宿街頭，更與女友渡過一起露宿的日子，一個睡袋兩份瞓。香港社區組織協會調查發現，露宿者有年輕化趨勢，近3成受訪者為35至44歲，比2015年同類全港性調查多1倍。<br />\n現年37歲青年阿Wing說，自少讀書差，多次留級，14歲中一時受同學欺凌，不再上學，16歲離家出走，卻因偷竊而被捕，曾短時間回家暫住，但因帶朋友上家偷東西，令家人不願配鎖匙給他，展開18年露宿生涯。他坦言，因有多次偷竊案底，一直難找工作，試過在麥當勞做了2年，有升職機會時，被發現有案底再度失業。"},{"pid":"8c08995f5c6e95dcedac7b427bfcabf71f1b67cf","tid":136946,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"咁都有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79476a3d3617c119e59f8cb552ac419199e01e2d","tid":136946,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca5106d8fc3c37fa2a0ab2b650bede5cb3f2489","tid":136946,"uid":16741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"37歲青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa5d10f166a95c16dfcc1064a217e07c595fa9d","tid":136946,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"37仲青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd225464692fbfd8bbc73e3cd30358c138283ff","tid":136946,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"35到44歲<br />\n青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁80歲咪中年？"},{"pid":"b4